participating-org.narrative:
The overall objective of the SPDH association: is to contribute to improving the well-being of the population by promoting democratic values, gender equality, strengthening peaceful coexistence, combating the violation of human rights, all forms of discriminationagainst the most vulnerable and socio-professional integration.

Specific objectives :
- Support for initiatives aimed at strengthening peace and establishing a genuine democracy and the emergence of a society respectful of human rights;
- Concretely integrate gender equality and the empowerment of rural women and indigenous people;
- Support for socio-professional integration and self-promotion of unemployed youth through the creation of trades and other income-generating activities;
 - Assist in the initiation and promotion of exchange frameworks, dialogues and discussions for a mass democratic culture;
- Promote peace through mediation and peacefulresolution of conflicts for good cohabitation;
 - Carry out support actions for demobilized persons with a view to their socio-professional integration.
